3 units
P210.1 Urban Planning Workshop
3 units
P213 Urban Planning Implementation
3 units
*P203 (Land Use Planning) is best taken during your first semester of enrollment instead of P299 (Research Methods in Planning), especially if you still have limited exposure to planning. For admission related details, please visit
UPOU website
."
